author: craigmcc
msg: Make the "group" attributes of each managed bean match the case of the
"type" attribute in generated MBean names, rather than being in all upper
case.

author: craigmcc
msg: Correct generation of MBean names for a Connector.  You need a "service="
component of the name to tell which Service the Connector belongs to.

author: craigmcc
msg: Fix a syntax error that causes the XML parse to fail.

author: remm
msg: - Fix a problem with auth constraints, where roles wouldn't get processed right.
For example, this would be failing:
<auth-constraint>
<role-name>foo</role-name>
<role-name>foo2</role-name>
<role-name>*</role-name>
</auth-constraint>
(Of course, 'foo' and 'foo2' really don't add anything, but it should still work).
